Title: Honoring Karen Carey upon the occasion of her retirement after 12 years of distinguished service as Market President and Chief Revenue Officer for Townsquare Media in Utica, New York
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION honoring Karen Carey for nearly 50 years of distinguished service to the media industry and upon the occasion of her retirement from Townsquare Media in Utica, New York, after serving 12 years as Market President and Chief Revenue Officer
